<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="opening-n">opening <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'əʊpnɪŋ/    美 /'oʊpnɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 孔；洞；缺口：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a narrow opening in the fence
篱笆上的小缺口</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] [常用单数] 开头；开端：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The movie has an exciting opening.
电影的开头非常令人兴奋。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c-u">3.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 开；开放：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>opening of</strong> a shop
店铺开张</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>opening hours</strong> / time
营业时间 / 开始营业时间</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>空缺</strong></h4></div>